    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches and minor dings, though there is no major structural damage. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear from regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though a thorough inspection might reveal some minor maintenance needs in the near future. It is a solid, honest vehicle for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
