    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car is in pristine, showroom condition, meticulously maintained with a flawless exterior and a spotless interior. It's a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands the very best in quality and performance. Experience the joy of driving a vehicle that is truly in perfect shape!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
